Steepest descent hill climb class that implements strictly greater.

Class for tournament selection where the best individual from a random sample size if found.

Class for trans-generational replacement with elitism where the best solutions in the population are kept and worst are removed.

Class which creates a file to track the final results of the trials for a given problem instance.
